collectors.title: Database
collectors.titleDetails: (9 total Queries, 9 of them unique across 3 Connections)

queries.sql: SELECT SUM(total_amount) as total_sales, COUNT(id) as total_orders, AVG(total_amount) as avg_order_value FROM orders WHERE payment_status = 'paid' AND status != 'cancelled' AND MONTH(ordered_at) = MONTH(CURRENT_DATE) AND YEAR(ordered_at) = YEAR(CURRENT_DATE)

SELECT DATE(ordered_at) as sale_date, SUM(total_amount) as total_daily_sales FROM orders WHERE payment_status = 'paid' AND status != 'cancelled' AND ordered_at >= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE, INTERVAL 30 DAY) GROUP BY DATE(ordered_at) ORDER BY sale_date ASC

SELECT mi.name as name, mi.price as price, SUM(oi.quantity) as total_quantity, COUNT(DISTINCT oi.order_id) as orders_count -- Count total times this item appeared in orders not using distinct FROM order_items oi JOIN menu_items mi ON oi.menu_item_id = mi.id JOIN orders o ON oi.order_id = o.id WHERE o.payment_status = 'paid' AND o.status != 'cancelled' AND o.ordered_at >= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE, INTERVAL 30 DAY) GROUP BY mi.id, mi.name, mi.price ORDER BY orders_count DESC -- ensures the right order, the most sold item is number 1 LIMIT 10

SELECT LOWER(payment_method) as payment_method, SUM(total_amount) as total_amount, COUNT(id) as transaction_count FROM orders WHERE payment_status = 'paid' AND status != 'cancelled' AND DATE(ordered_at) = CURRENT_DATE GROUP BY payment_method

SELECT o.id, o.total_amount, o.status, o.ordered_at, o.payment_method, rt.table_number, GROUP_CONCAT(mi.name SEPARATOR ', ') AS items FROM orders o LEFT JOIN restaurant_tables rt ON o.table_id = rt.id LEFT JOIN order_items oi ON oi.order_id = o.id LEFT JOIN menu_items mi ON mi.id = oi.menu_item_id WHERE 1=1 GROUP BY o.id ORDER BY o.ordered_at DESC LIMIT 10

SELECT HOUR(ordered_at) as hour, COUNT(id) as total_orders, SUM(total_amount) as total_sales FROM orders WHERE payment_status = 'paid' AND status != 'cancelled' AND DATE(ordered_at) = CURRENT_DATE GROUP BY hour ORDER BY total_sales DESC LIMIT 5
